{"tid":921638,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"南韓女團MAMAMOO 新歌向香港七八十年代電影致敬！","createTime":"2018-11-29T17:16:24.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-01T08:02:08.000Z","uid":74065,"like":87,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"b7dcdc0129470b8a2a52e8939c28ef98e4b51136","tid":921638,"uid":74065,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-29T17:16:24.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=f6hLRn1Yq2Y\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3Df6hLRn1Yq2Y&d=1LWwu1L6ebsTUj17mC%2FiJLDFWuQMdHqkD4FeOi%2BWxPk%3D&h=9d48ba29\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=f6hLRn1Yq2Y</a><br />\n南韓女團MAMAMOO 新歌 - WIND FLOWER<br />\n<br />\n透過預告照和視頻，不難發現成員們的穿著、姿勢、動作和拍攝場地，與一些香港電影場面頗相似！特別是MV預告中，粉絲們認為很多畫面是從王家衛導演的作品系列中出現過呢~ 粉絲們也發現MV導演的個人IG提到在正拍攝「7080香港」的MV，並列下張曼玉、張國榮、梅艷芳和關之琳的名字，看來是將四名代表人物作為參考吧？<br />\n<img src=\"http://img.focussy.com/sharingSub/1811/so1318743377525513802646.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.focussy.com%2FsharingSub%2F1811%2Fso1318743377525513802646.jpg&h=d96277ee&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><ins>玟星、頌樂計程車靠肩場面 - 《春光乍洩》、《花樣年華》</ins></strong><br />\n<img src=\"http://img.focussy.com/sharingSub/1811/so1318743377530193813200.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.focussy.com%2FsharingSub%2F1811%2Fso1318743377530193813200.jpg&h=1165c6dd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<strong><ins>輝人鐵絲網圍欄場面 - 《重慶森林》</ins></strong><br />\n<img src=\"http://img.focussy.com/sharingSub/1811/so1318743377533313824396.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.focussy.com%2FsharingSub%2F1811%2Fso1318743377533313824396.jpg&h=d17d672c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<strong><ins>華莎對著鏡子舞蹈場面 - 《春光乍洩》</ins></strong><br />\n<img src=\"http://img.focussy.com/sharingSub/1811/so1318743377539553835308.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.focussy.com%2FsharingSub%2F1811%2Fso1318743377539553835308.jpg&h=d9be8334&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<strong><ins>玟星茶餐廳場面 - 《墮落天使》</ins></strong><br />\n<img src=\"http://img.focussy.com/sharingSub/1811/so1318743377541113836667.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.focussy.com%2FsharingSub%2F1811%2Fso1318743377541113836667.jpg&h=553c2949&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<strong><ins>輝人望著魚缸里的葵百合花場面 - 《重慶森林》</ins></strong><br />\n<img src=\"http://img.focussy.com/sharingSub/1811/so1318743377544233847862.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.focussy.com%2FsharingSub%2F1811%2Fso1318743377544233847862.jpg&h=c3e3c83e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<strong><ins>頌樂擦掉口紅場面 - 《霸王別姬》（注：該電影由陳凱歌執導）</ins></strong><br />\n<img src=\"http://img.focussy.com/sharingSub/1811/so1318743377548913858416.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.focussy.com%2FsharingSub%2F1811%2Fso1318743377548913858416.jpg&h=56ec0157&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<strong><ins>頌樂預告照 - 《花樣年華》</ins></strong><br />\n<img src=\"http://img.focussy.com/sharingSub/1811/so1318743377552033859612.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.focussy.com%2FsharingSub%2F1811%2Fso1318743377552033859612.jpg&h=bf5ed6a7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n除了在MV預告和個人照發現許多王家衛導演所拍攝過的畫面，粉絲們也找到MAMAMOO首度預告發片日期的照片，也似乎跟王導的作品有所關聯哦！當大家以為速食店的LOGO是代表MAMAMOO時，原來這品牌的速食店也出現在兩部王家衛導演的作品中！<br />\n<img src=\"http://img.focussy.com/sharingSub/1811/so13187433775551538610807.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.focussy.com%2FsharingSub%2F1811%2Fso13187433775551538610807.jpg&h=405f7dbc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n在《墮落天使》和《重慶森林》中，男主角的身影出現在速食店內，抖大的LOGO引入眼簾，讓人印象非常深刻。<br />\n<img src=\"http://img.focussy.com/sharingSub/1811/so131874337755827386112.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.focussy.com%2FsharingSub%2F1811%2Fso131874337755827386112.jpg&h=4420915c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n雖然MV導演並沒有提到MV中是否參考了港產片，或是向王家衛導演致敬的MV，但從粉絲們鷹眼的發現，似乎真有此事呢~太多的巧合啦~！迫不及待看到完整版的MV，說不定還會有更多新發現哦！"},{"pid":"237bd099eada4f3a4532c60b0d0b31ba47a5e2a9","tid":921638,"uid":555,"like":0,"dislike":6,"score":-6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-29T17:17:21.000Z","msg":"Mamamoo me wife"},{"pid":"cc611a586cc29628d0b5a9beac9490913644b5ee","tid":921638,"uid":202131,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-29T17:20:29.000Z","msg":"首歌係好聽，但係就唔多似主打囉，唔知南韓個邊受唔受，希望今次藍專成績好啦"},{"pid":"4da68b83ddfe27be6b5413e3265752a4a81d6127","tid":921638,"uid":86236,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-29T17:23:28.000Z","msg":"respect respect<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d7b45aedd64f58aedf26007be0baf1aa59191fd9","tid":921638,"uid":52073,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-29T17:28:04.000Z","msg":"哥哥真係好撚型阿<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"acb966bad916ce4f4c38e197a58cb4e2cdf6fd99","tid":921638,"uid":52073,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d7b45aedd64f58aedf26007be0baf1aa59191fd9","tid":921638,"uid":52073,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-29T17:28:04.000Z","msg":"哥哥真係好撚型阿<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-29T17:28:19.000Z","msg":"我娛樂台oppa"},{"pid":"e3319698ef872bdacdd98479fa6a87bbeb66c906","tid":921638,"uid":74065,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"acb966bad916ce4f4c38e197a58cb4e2cdf6fd99","tid":921638,"uid":52073,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d7b45aedd64f58aedf26007be0baf1aa59191fd9","tid":921638,"uid":52073,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-29T17:28:04.000Z","msg":"哥哥真係好撚型阿<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-29T17:2